nightmare about it ever since.

359
00:56:50.369 --> 00:56:51.370
Who have you told this to?

360
00:56:53.455 --> 00:56:54.289
Just you.

361
00:56:56.500 --> 00:56:58.210
Why did you choose this profession?

362
